Whether you wish to relax on the beach or enjoy entertaining family activities, the Abama Resort can accommodate you. When you reserve your stay, you'll be able to rest comfortably in one of the 469 suites or secluded villas.  The Abama Resort provides warm, sunny weather thanks to Tenerife's island location. The panoramic view of the Atlantic Ocean along with the island's vegetation juxtaposed with the tough volcanic landscape gives you a spectacular natural experience along with your luxury accommodations.While staying at the Abama Resort, you'll be surrounded by booming banana plantations along with the white sandy shores that sprawl across the 160 hectares of land that the Abama Resort inhabits. The Abama Resort offers a number of deluxe hotel rooms along with several private villas.  When you retire to your hotel room, you'll be greeted by cultured North African design ideas along with gorgeous views of the crisp Atlantic Ocean.  The accessible villas give you the luxury you'd expect from the Ritz-Carlton while still supplying you with seclusion.While enjoying your stay in the fivestar hotel, you will be able to make the most of the different facilities the resort offers.While on vacation, you can enjoy playing tennis, swimming, eating out, or dancing the night away in the bars and nightclubs.If you enjoy golf or want to learn to play, you can take advantage of the resort's golf school and golf course.In order to provide you with the best possible charges, The Ritz-Carlton Abama Resort has joined forces with Design Holidays.Whether you're planning to book a family holiday, a honeymoon, or a fun trip with buddies, contact the Design Holidays booking team.To request additional information regarding the Abama Resort or even to book your holiday excursion, contact us on 01444 87 2200 or simply look on the resort's website.
